name: Cucumber Tea Sandwiches
author: Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps®
summary: Snack Factory® Pretzel Crisps® Minis are topped with a cucumber slice, a bit of cream cheese, and a dusting of dill then topped with another mini for bite-size tea sandwiches.
ingredients: 24  Snack Factory® Gluten Free Original Pretzel Crisps® Minis
1 (4 ounce) package cream cheese, softened, or more as needed
directions: Cut slices of cucumber into thirds or quarters
Place on half of the Gluten Free Original Pretzel Crisps® Minis
Spread or pipe cream cheese on top of cucumbers, then sprinkle with dill
Top with another mini to make itty bitty gluten free tea sandwiches
